    "date": "2020-06-12T13:43:25Z",
    "text": "Workforce Investment Disclosure Act of 2020\n\nThis bill requires an issuer of securities to disclose certain information regarding human capital management policies, practices, and performance. This information includes workforce data related to\n\n full-time, part-time, and contingent employees; turnover and retention rates; racial, ethnic, and gender composition; skills, training, and capabilities; health and safety; compensation and incentives; and recruiting."
